skills and conquer your opponents on the battlefield.\n\nThe arena is set. Fighting is the only way out.\nAre you up to the challenge?", "short_description": "X8 is the FREE TO PLAY next generation Hero Shooter!\n\nExecuting its directive to assemble worthy opponents, the rogue mod X8 has collected characters from across different game franchises. Players embody a variety of heroes and engage in 5v5 VR battles to restore a path back to their worlds."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "X8_LU7_Cover_Icon_512x512.png", "id": "1700672760771542", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982690_1700672764104875_1201346064423233571_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Hkb-V_JZ1N0Q7kNvgGac4NV&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCqNRD--yjzHtKvhP05-lrY7O0z-aa-RDTblHqZeF9DxQ&oe=6703C073"}, {"file_name": "pub_x8_Logo_556x164.png", "id": "1698286060574850", "image_type": "APP_IMG_IMMERSIVE_LAYER_LOGO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031543_1698286063908183_7870509160302259884_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=y135t1XfPVEQ7kNvgGrZcIn&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC_6SeYOYh1lsiCXPJndWAPDFb_Vfhv82loM48kmrer_A&oe=6703AF48"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "1601022513728602", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984463_1601022517061935_7590174127011369459_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=s_c1F-H3PfkQ7kNvgFdLG2t&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBiWXBKyI2OmElTfHNiwWLMf8xInomFstM5dwLqt-Vwkg&oe=6703B250"}, {"file_name": "X8_LU7_Square_1440x1440.png", "id": "1256150292055401", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035430_1256150295388734_6637746793680017730_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=BkUBXCR2aZQQ7kNvgGB_WM4&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBWRVBuROyR5CaiCMXEAcp2HfoY